parameters: Welcome to Elmo Village! Where did you ladies come from?

Our specialty is called Chao Roast, which is a sauted dish
with pork and mushrooms. You should try eating it while
you're here!

There was a pervert who loved mushrooms in the past... They
researched mushrooms so much that it became a local
specialty. But as a result, they ended up being poisoned...

\SE[2] Ahh, a souvenir for the two of you, huh... Well, I
guess it wouldn't hurt to prepare something.
\SE[33]...though, I wonder what would be good.

\SE[47]The specialty of this village is mushroom cuisine,
but it's not suitable as a souvenir.... \SE[38]...We don't
have anything like that either.

\SE[2]Feelings... That's true, huh... \SE[34]But if we don't
have a budget, there's nothing we can do about it. We'll
have to start with earning pocket money....
\SE[6]What's wrong, Uncle? You seem a bit down today.

\SE[52]... Ah, the ship broke, huh... Well, I guess that
can't be helped. \SE[21] Things with a form will eventually
break, after all.

That's true... This should still be rideable if I fix it.
But... my wife is against repairing it...

Quit being a sailor if you can't make any money! ...is what
he said? He's saying that you can earn more if you get a job
in Cordain! ...what a thoughtless remark.

But I know, damn it!! He's hooked on those city hosts...!!
He's using my money to drink with other men!!

...I'm exhausted. My family is like this, I might not be
able to have a ship, and my daughter tells me not to wash
the laundry together...

Maybe I should just sink to the bottom of the sea with this
ship... After all, there's no one left who would mourn my
absence...
\SE[38] No, it's over. There's nothing we can do about it.

Ah, after talking, I've made up my mind. Let's die together
from now on. With this momentum, we can do it. We can do it
with this momentum.

This feeling in my heart... It's great! I feel a sense of
accomplishment from making a decision after a long time!
Alright! I'm going to die so that I won't be a burden to
everyone...!!

\SE[59]No, no! You really shouldn't do that...! \SE[51]If
you do that, nothing good will come out of it!

...Suddenly, my feelings have cooled down. Why was I so
desperate to die just a moment ago...?

However, as a result, I'm getting angry at my wife!! But if
I talk back, I'll get punched... Damn it! How am I supposed
to relieve this stress?!
\SE[39]No, no... We can't just leave it like this, can we...

\SE[21]Shall we... refresh ourselves? \SE[46]I just want a
little allowance for it.

No, for a moment, I thought it would be good... but... I
can't do that after all. I have a daughter, and I got
married with various preparations, you know...

Now that I look closely, Melissa resembles the girl from my
first love... Ah, Sheena-chan who went to Caudine. She was a
girl who cooked energetically... I wonder if she's still
doing well even now...

Ronoa resembles the child I liked before becoming an
adult... That child also went to work in Yuriseen... Yes,
Mira-chan... I wonder if she's doing well too...

...No, maybe I should ask after all... Riding a bicycle
while thinking about the girl I used to like in the past
feels luxurious. Uncle is also starting to feel better
somehow...

\SE[16]Thank you very much. \.Even though we don't have any
real action, is it okay? \!\SE[45]Instead, I'll do my best
to fulfill your requests, but...

Yeah, I know. It's probably fine as long as it's around that
level without feeling guilty. Do you have a place to stay?
Since I don't have a wife right now...
\SE[57]I see... Well, if that's the condition...

A little while ago, you know. Some girls moved in from
outside. I immediately became their friend! Isn't that
impressive?!

This village, there's nothing here, right? I'm a little torn
about whether to go to Yurisene or not. But leaving my
father behind... I don't know. Hey, what do you think?

That's true. But, it's only one life, you know... I kind of
want to be surrounded by handsome guys in the city....

City Mount...!!? How dare you! There are plenty of good
places even in this countryside!!
It's an old doghouse. It seems to be well taken care of...
